ollapse\">\n                    <ul class=\"nav navbar-nav navbar-right\">\n                        <!-- ADD MENU LINKS HERE. THESE ARE NON-FUNCTIONAL EXAMPLES. -->\n                        <li><a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\">Our Store</a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/usr/dealsonlywebstore\">About Us</a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"https://contact.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?ContactUserNextGen&amp;recipient=dealsonlywebstore\">Contact Us</a></li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div><!--/.nav-collapse -->\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                <div>\n                    <div class=\"main-image\">\n                        <img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/7213/combo_complete.jpg?expires=1752789599&amp;signature=a19ab1fa255b785c4416cddc5e879f530daf39501654ac73db903b6bd052503c\" class=\"img-responsive\" alt=\"Responsive image\">\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <h3>Product Details</h3>\n                <!-- ADD A NEW ROW FOR EACH PRODUCT ATTRIBUTE YOU WANT TO SHOW IN THE TABLE OR YOU CAN REMOVE THE TABLE COMPLETELY-->\n                <div class=\"product-specs\">\n                    <table>\n                        <tbody>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\">MPN:</td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right\">ASRO5GCS</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\">UPC:</td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right\">706569447958</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">5 GALLON CLASSIFIER SCREEN: Soil sifting mesh classifiers will fit on top of 5 gallon bucket and our 14\" gold pan; Interlocking, stackable design;&nbsp; Top Diameter: 13.25\", Bottom Diameter: 11\"</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">RUGGED DESIGN: Constructed from High-Impact Durable Plastic with 304 Stainless Steel Wire Mesh</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">CLASSIFIER SIFTING SCREEN SIZE: 1/100\", 1/70\", 1/20\", 1/8\", 1/2\"</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">GOLD PROSPECTING EQUIPMENT: Classifying your raw material down is imperative for successful gold recovery; removing large and worthless rocks from your high-yielding pay dirt</td><td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">FIELD TESTED: Easily screen off gravel and rock from your findings to locate gold and other treasures hidden within your raw material</td></tr>\n                        </tbody>\n                    </table>\n                </div><!-- /product-specs -->\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                <h1>ASR Outdoor 5pc Gold Panning Classifier Screen Set, Mesh Soil Sifter</h1>\n                <h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">275.99</span></h2>\n                <p>The ASR Outdoor Gold Panning Classifier Screens are a must-have for gold prospecting and mineral recovery. Utilizing our high-impact steel wire soil sifting pans is one of the first steps in successful gold prospecting. \n\nThe Classifier Soil Sifting Screens will aid your recovery efforts by separating unwanted coarse raw material into finer, manageable good material ready to wash in your gold pan or run through a sluice box.\n\nAvailable in 9 different sizes for both fine and coarse material sifting, ensuring you'll be able to properly sift all size material. \n\nEach soil classifying screen will fit over a standard 5 gallon bucket as well as a 14\" gold pan and they are stackable, interlocking on top of each other to ensure that they will not slip or slide when used in conjunction with one another. \n\nProper classification of material by size is the key to more efficient gold separation. This is true for roughing out your material, all the way to the final step of fine gold separation. Using a gold sifter screen is essential for gold panning, sluicing or running a high banker well.\n \nSeparating and processing your gold concentrates by size with a classifier makes gold recovery much more efficient and less labor intensive, is faster and a more effective, resulting in more gold!</p>\n                <div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n                    <div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n                    <div class=\"grid-100\">\n                        <p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n                        <p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n                        <a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&amp;sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n                        </a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n                <p>© 2025</p>\n            </div> <!-- /footer -->\n    \n        </div> <!-- /container -->\n        <div style=\"clear:both\">\n            &nbsp;<table></table>\n      